// 3개 역할 관계 테스트

// Give 관계 정의
Give IS RELATION
Give HAS Giver (Node)
Give HAS Receiver (Node)
Give HAS Gift (Node)
Give DO
    Giver LOSES IS Gift
    Receiver IS Gift
END

// 아이템 정의
Potion IS Item
Potion HAS Name "Health Potion"

// 캐릭터 정의
Player IS Character
Player IS Potion
Player HAS Name "Hero"

NPC IS Character
NPC HAS Name "Merchant"

// 초기 상태 - Player가 Potion을 가지고 있음
DEBUG GRAPH

// Give 실행: Player가 NPC에게 Potion을 줌
Player Give NPC Potion

// 결과: NPC가 Potion을 가짐
DEBUG GRAPH
